<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Send to kindle</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-BmbxuPwQa2lc/FVzBcNJ7UAyJxM6wuqIj61tLrc4wSX0szH/Ev+nYRRuWlolflfl"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav id="navbar">
      <h1>Send File to Kindle</h1>
    </nav>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
      <div id="conteiner">
        <form action="/sendEmail" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" style="width: 100%; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px; height: 100%">
          <div class="input-group flex-nowrap">
            <span class="input-group-text" id="addon-wrapping">
              Email para enviar
            </span>
            <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Email" aria-label="Email" aria-describedby="addon-wrapping"/>
          </div>
          <br />
          <label class="d-flex justify-content-center" id="inputArea">
            <input type="file" name="fileUpload" id="File" onchange="changeNameFile()"/>
            <div class="align-middle" id="nameInputArea">Escolha o arquivo ou arrate aqui</div>
          </label>
          <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-6 mx-auto">
            <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mt-3" value="Enviar" />
          </div>
          <div style="color: red; margin-bottom: 0%; text-align: center;">
            <%= typeof msg != 'undefined' ? msg : '' %>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="fs-1">Tutorial</div> 

      <div class="m-5">

        <div class="m-3"><strong>Passo 1.</strong> Abra a <a href="https://www.amazon.com.br/hz/mycd/myx#/home/settings/payment" target="_blank">amazon</a></div> 
        <img src="./assets/main.jpg" class="img-fluid" style="width: 90%; margin-top: 15px;">

      </div>

      <hr>

      <div class="m-5">

        <div class="m-3"><strong>Passo 2.</strong> Verifique e adicione os email aprovados</div>
        <img src="./assets/seta.jpg" class="img-fluid" style="width: 60%;">

        <div class="m-3"> Adicione o email <strong>SendFileToKindle@gmail.com</strong></div>
        <img src="./assets/addEmail.jpg" style="width: 60%;">

      </div>

      <hr>

      <div class="m-5">

        <div class="m-3"> <strong>Passo 3.</strong> Pegue o email do seu Kindle e adicione no campo <strong>Email para enviar</strong>, note que sempre termina com <strong>@kindle.com</strong></div>
        <img src="./assets/focado1.jpg" style="width: 90%; height: 150px;">

      </div>

      <hr>

      <div class="m-5">

        <div class="mt-3"> 
          <strong>Passo 4.</strong> Selecione o arquivo para enviar e Verifique os tipos de arquivos aceitos: 
          <strong>
            .doc, 
            .docx, 
            .rtf, 
            .htm,
            .html,
            .txt, 
            .jpg,
            .gif,
            .bmp,
            .png,
            .pdf,
            .mobi,
            .rtf, 
            .prc,
            .psz,
            .azw. 

        </strong>

        </div>

      </div>

      <hr>

      <div class="m-5">

        <div class="m-5"> <strong>Passo 5.</strong> Envie o arquivo para o email do seu kindle, verifique seu email se a<strong> amazon </strong>pedio alguma permis√£o de envio. </div>

      </div>

    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
